Class Skill

  • java.lang.Object

    @Entity(name="Skill")
public class Skill
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Skill data model. Represents a quality a resource can have and that a project can require. Having a certain skill allows a resource to fulfill a requirement.
